{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was going on till, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] until June, I think, June and July.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to-- you know, we used to go down to the, to the main camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had loafs of bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, I don't know how big, it's like a loaf like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to-- everybody used to get, like, a eighth of-- you know, like they cut it up in eight pieces.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they used to sometimes choose me to go down and bring up the, the bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they used to make some soup there, and to bring out the soup on the field, that we would, you know, eat there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes we had to go down to the, to the kitchen, to the dining room there, [INAUDIBLE] whatever, to the main-- and a lot of times, they brought up on the, on the field, and we had there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was so horrible, this food, that I [INAUDIBLE] when I happened to see how they made this food in the evening, it was so bad, and I was so hungry and this.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I couldn't eat this food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to take, you know, leaves from, from the cabbage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were big worms there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to chop it up, you know, and make a soup out of it, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there is a lot, a lot in between that, you know, is just-- it's just hard to explain everything, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's such a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'm just telling you what comes to my mind, to what I can remember more vivid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And just a week, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yeah, there was a lot of talk because they, they terminated, already, one concentration camp there nearby.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
